# Free Ebooks Prologue
These ebooks are from WikiSource which provides CC BY-SA 4.0 (Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International) license for all it's content. These files are used to generate presage database to provide word prediction for lomiri-keyboard for Ubuntu Touch.

